    {
      "id": "1b74b581-204c-4d6c-82ee-d225903def0c",
      "name": "Sticky Note b72ab057",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -688,
        -96
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 560,
        "height": 1956,
        "content": "# Coach fitness and nutrition on Telegram with Claude, Google Sheets and Calendar\n\n# 📥  [Open full documentation on Notion](https://automatisation.notion.site/Coach-fitness-and-nutrition-on-Telegram-with-Claude-Google-Sheets-and-Calendar-Course-support-En-3993d6550fd9810c9641ffc68da1d2aa)\n\n## How it works\n1. The workflow triggers when a Telegram message arrives (text or voice note).\n2. Voice notes are downloaded from Telegram and transcribed with OpenAI.\n3. The message, chat ID and current date are normalized into common fields.\n4. An AI coach agent (Anthropic Claude) with session memory answers in French and decides when to call its tools.\n5. Google Sheets tools read and write the user profile, workout history, nutrition journal and weekly plans.\n6. A Google Calendar tool schedules workout sessions on request.\n7. The coach reply is sent back to the user on Telegram.\n\n## Setup\n1. Connect your Telegram bot credential on the trigger, download and reply nodes.\n2. Connect Anthropic (chat model) and OpenAI (voice transcription) credentials.\n3. Connect Google Sheets OAuth2 and Google Calendar OAuth2 credentials.\n4. Create one Google Spreadsheet with 5 tabs: profil (id_telegram, poids_actuel, objectif), historique (id_telegram, date, exercice, performance), nutrition (id_telegram, date, repas, calories, proteines, lipides, glucides), plan_nutrition (id_telegram, date_maj, plan_repas, liste_courses), plan_sport (id_telegram, date_maj, programme_texte).\n5. Select this spreadsheet in every Google Sheets tool node and pick your calendar in the Calendar tool.\n6. Adjust the variables in the Configuration node (language, date format, memory length).\n\n## Requirements\n- A Telegram bot token (create one with @BotFather).\n- An Anthropic API key for the coach model.\n- An OpenAI API key for audio transcription.\n- A Google account with Sheets and Calendar access.\n\n## Customization\n- Edit the system prompt of the AI fitness coach agent to change the coaching style.\n- Change the language, date format or memory window in the Configuration node.\n- Swap the Anthropic model for another chat model, or add more Google Sheets tools (measurements, sleep, hydration).\n- Add a text-to-speech step to reply with voice notes.\n\n## Need help customizing?\nContact me for consulting and support : [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/in/doctor-firass/)\n\n# MY NEW YOUTUBE CHANNEL\n👉 [Subscribe to my new YouTube channel](https://www.youtube.com/@DrFiras_AI). Here I'll share videos and Shorts with practical tutorials and FREE templates for n8n.\n\n[![The AI Doctor](https://www.dr-firas.com/the-ai-doctor.png)](https://www.youtube.com/@DrFiras_AI)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
